title: Glary utilities 4.8 with serials UPDATEABLE
description:
Since Glary decided to block the old serials you have to install an older version of the program, use the serial and then update. Serial is just to unlock the pro version, and is not affected by future updates.

1.	Install the older version of the program (v4.8 or older)
2.	Do not update when prompted
3.	Use serials 0788-61679-5808226 or 078861679-5880293. Make up your own name.
4.	After you unlock pro, update software
5.	Enjoy!


And please seed
